  "response_text": "A white claw-foot bathtub sits in a softly lit bathroom with teal-blue wall tiles and a matching tiled floor. Behind it is a large window with pale blinds, and small bottles in pink and yellow tones rest along the ledge near a silver faucet. To the right, a vase of light-colored flowers sits on a small table, adding a decorative domestic touch. The tub is empty and glossy, with rounded edges and curved feet, and it gradually fills more of the scene as attention moves toward its rim and interior.\n\nThe product appears in a close view: a white plastic bottle with a green cap and a large green label reading “Soft Scrub with Bleach cleanser,” with the Clorox logo near the top. A hand holds or moves the bottle close to the viewer. Small on-screen text at the bottom reads, “Use only as directed.” The bottle tips away, and the view changes to a close-up of a purple, porous sponge held in a hand. From the green-tipped bottle, a thick white line of cleanser is squeezed onto the sponge in a wavy stripe.\n\nA hand then presses the purple sponge against the inside of the white bathtub and scrubs a slightly dull or stained area. The sponge moves in firm strokes along the curved inner wall, leaving the surface looking smooth and bright. The hand continues wiping along the tub’s rounded edge near the window, moving the sponge back and forth across the glossy white rim. The bathroom setting remains the same, with the teal tiles, window, faucet, and small bottles visible behind the action.\n\nNear the end, the bathtub is seen from a low angle on the tiled floor, making its claw feet look almost animated and character-like. Two cleaning products stand in front of it: the Soft Scrub bottle on the left and a cylindrical powder cleanser can on the right. Small text along the bottom reads, “Not all powders are harsh.” The tub’s feet shift in position, and in the following view the powder cleanser is gone while the Soft Scrub bottle remains beside the tub, visually favored by the tub-like character.\n\nThe final image places the Soft Scrub with Bleach bottle prominently in the foreground on the blue tiled floor, with the white claw-foot tub looming behind it. Large white on-screen text across the upper part of the image reads, “Preferred By Tubs Everywhere.”",
